，面积{{convert|1.25|sqmi|sqkm|2}}<ref name ="Gazetteer files">{{cite web|title=US Gazetteer files 2010|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|publisher=[[美国人口普查局|美国人口普查局]]|accessdate=2013-01-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/699nOulzi?url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|archive-date=2012-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，人口3,615人（[[2010年美国人口普查|2010年美国人口普查]]）<ref name="Census 2010">{{Cite web| url=http://factfinder2.census.gov| title=Profile of General Population and Housing Characteristics: 2010 Demographic Profile Data (DP-1): Greenhills village, Ohio| publisher=U.S. Census Bureau, American Factfinder| accessdate=2012-11-01| archive-date=2013-09-11| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130911234518/http://factfinder2.census.gov/| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

